## 📌 What is this repo?

This is my **Engineering Track submission** for the Kalvium Capstone program.

It is **not a demo app**. It is a documented record of how I approached real engineering problems — milestone by milestone — using the **PERN Stack** (PostgreSQL, Express, React, Node.js).

Each milestone in this repo represents:
- A real decision I had to make
- A problem I had to solve
- A system I had to design — not just code

