## 🏗️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| Frontend | React (Hooks + Context API) | Component-driven, scalable UI |
| Backend | Node.js + Express.js | Lightweight, fast REST server |
| Database | PostgreSQL | Relational integrity, complex queries |
| Auth | JWT + Bcrypt | Stateless, secure authentication |
| Testing | Postman + manual edge cases | API contract validation |
| Dev Tools | Git, GitHub, VS Code | Version control, collaboration |

---

## ⚙️ System Architecture

```
┌─────────────┐        ┌──────────────┐        ┌──────────────────┐
│   React UI  │ ──────▶│  Express API │ ──────▶│   PostgreSQL DB  │
│  (Client)   │◀────── │  (Server)    │◀────── │   (Data Layer)   │
└─────────────┘        └──────────────┘        └──────────────────┘
       │                      │
       │                ┌─────┴──────┐
       │                │ Middleware │
       │                │ JWT Auth   │
       │                │ Error Hand │
       └────────────────┴────────────┘
```

**Request Lifecycle:**
```
Client Request
  → Route Handler
    → Auth Middleware (JWT verify)
      → Controller (input validation)
        → Service Layer (business logic)
          → Model / DB Query
            → Response (JSON)
```

